Northwest Airlines to cut some fares . Northwest Airlines Corp said Monday it was offering fare cuts of up to 55 percent on select days to most destinations . The fare sale is for travel between August 25 and December 16 , the airline said . Fares from the United States to London have been cut as much as 35 percent , Northwest said . Domestic fares must be purchased by August 21 . Passengers can save most traveling Tuesday , Wednesday or Saturday , Northwest said . All fares are non - refundable and must be purchased at least 14 days before departure , the company said . Northwest shares were down 1 / 16 at 40 Monday . ( ( - - Chicago newsdesk , 312 - 408 - 8787 ) ) 
